==Bundles==
Cinder Shard is not used in any [[bundles]].

==Trading==
Cinder Shards can be traded for goods and recipes at the [[Island Trader]] and the Dwarf shop in the [[Volcano Dungeon#Shop|Volcano Dungeon]].
