==Tailoring==
It is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create {{name|Sunglasses|class=inline}}. It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as an orange dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
7 Cinder Shards are requested by [[Stingray]] in a [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quest]] to increase the capacity of the pond from 3 to 5.

